Drr6_zikuZQ.title: Voice Tech in Star Trek: TNG Supercut | Season 5
Drr6_zikuZQ.author: Nick Felker
Drr6_zikuZQ.description: This is a supercut of all the voice interactions between characters and a computer that occur in Star Trek: The Next Generation, Season 5. Each clip is cut to focus solely on the conversation. If you want more context, I'd recommend watching the series in its entirety.
